                            <div class="pb60">
                                <div class="mainHd">Dean's Word</div>
                                <div class="flexBox deanWordBox1">
                                    <div class="left">
                                        <img src="/ust_website_university_study/static/src/images/dean-img2.jpg"
                                             alt=""/>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="textBox right">
                                        Praise be to God, Lord of the Worlds, and prayers and peace be upon the honest
                                        and trustworthy our master Muhammad and all his family and companions, and
                                        after:
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        At the outset, I welcome all visitors to the website of the College of
                                        Engineering and Computers at the University of Science and Technology.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        The college provides modern and diverse programs in engineering fields, which
                                        include civil engineering, architecture, biomedical engineering, mechatronics
                                        engineering, as well as in the fields of computers, information technology,
                                        information systems, graphic design and multimedia to obtain a bachelor's
                                        degree. This is in addition to the master's program in computing.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        The college invested thanks to the continuous support provided by the university
                                        leadership represented by the university president, to work on equipping
                                        laboratories and workshops, as well as advanced laboratories in all engineering
                                        and computer fields,
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flexBox justifyContentBetween deanWordBox2">
                                    <div class="textBox left">
                                        and classrooms laboratories in all engineering and computer fields, and
                                        classrooms equipped with modern technologies, activating educational strategies
                                        and focusing on educational curricula and cadres in order to keep pace with
                                        engineering and computer development and prepare them To be among the future
                                        makers, elite academics who are distinguished in their scientific fields
                                        contribute to this. The college is also keen to achieve high standards of
                                        quality and accreditation, as the programs under this college have been
                                        developed according to a scientific methodology that meets the needs of the
                                        local and regional labor market and in accordance with the standards approved by
                                        the academic accreditation organization, and the college is now preparing and
                                        preparing for the rest of the accreditation requirements according to a plan
                                        prepared in advance for this purpose.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        The mission of the college is not limited to preparing students to enter the
                                        labor market, but extends beyond their graduation by providing them with the
                                        professional and cognitive skills necessary to meet all forms of challenges in
                                        engineering, industrial and computer sciences,
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="textBox right">
                                        which qualifies them to lead in the fields of creativity and engineering and
                                        computer innovation committed to professional ethics.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        If you are looking for a unique university study experience in one of the best
                                        engineering and computer colleges at the local and regional levels, I invite you
                                        to the college to explore the study opportunities we offer, or visit the college
                                        website to get the information you are looking for.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        I ask God Almighty to help us to advance this ancient scientific edifice and for
                                        the college to be a beacon and a model to guide students and society for a
                                        better path towards a more beautiful future.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        In conclusion, I thank you once again for your visit to the Faculty of
                                        Engineering and Computers website, and we hope you will repeat your visit to
                                        this website and continue your communication with the Faculty, its
                                        administration and faculty members.
                                        <br/>
                                        <br/>
                                        Dean of the College
                                        <br/>
                                        Assistant Dr. Nasr Al-Saqqaf
